# 2025-12-04 23:06:50.919187
+Ok, now - we need to write a compiler. This compiler takes a component set, a module name and creates a src/{module_name}/__init.py and src/module/main.py which has the component entry point in main and imports a file in /src/{module_name}/{uniqified(component_name)}.py each dependency it has will also have to be in the directory and those symbols imported, and so forth transitively. write the .md specification file for this copmiler. Do not write code. 

# 2025-12-04 23:18:44.462910
