# 2025-12-04 23:24:52.753977
+We will need edits to these files to link back to the original component so the UID should be stored in a comment at the beginning of the file. Add this to the specification. Also, we will need to add an additional feature to the components. Components can have a "path" designation which introduces a new directory of which they sit inside. The path designation will help hierarchical components from cluttering the main module. Each sub folder will need however a new __init__.py added.  This compiler will of course only work for python. In order to group the logical files, they should be called {unique_component_name_1}_logical.py and imported automatically at the beginning of the implementation. When we resync from edits they shold move from the file back to the source component - same with the logical implementation. 

# 2025-12-04 23:30:17.999765
